    "UID" -> Null, "Notebook" -> "011059f3-84fe-45dc-81c3-8519e79c4ee8"|>, 
   <|"Data" -> "# Release notes *3.0.3*\n\nThu 2 Apr 2026 12:02:14", 
    "Display" -> "markdown", "Hash" -> 
     "0d6cf8ac-12fa-4670-a55f-886886a74279", "Invisible" -> False, 
    "MetaOnly" -> False, "Props" -> <||>, "PublicFields" -> {"Properties"}, 
    "State" -> "Idle", "Type" -> "Output", "UID" -> Null, 
    "Notebook" -> "011059f3-84fe-45dc-81c3-8519e79c4ee8"|>, 
   <|"Data" -> ".md\n## Window Throttling\nWe fixed unintended window \
throttling on some machines, when it is not focused or hidden. This is \
crucial for a long-living applications such as monitors (lab equipment), \
where some data has to be updated continuously for hours or days. ", 
    "Display" -> "codemirror", "Hash" -> 
     "f338ed0c-a2da-4eae-b034-5cad13d31963", "Invisible" -> False, 
    "MetaOnly" -> False, "Props" -> <|"Hidden" -> True|>, 
    "PublicFields" -> {"Properties"}, "State" -> "Idle", "Type" -> "Input", 
    "UID" -> Null, "Notebook" -> "011059f3-84fe-45dc-81c3-8519e79c4ee8"|>, 
   <|"Data" -> "## Window Throttling\nWe fixed unintended window throttling \
on some machines, when it is not focused or hidden. This is crucial for a \
long-living applications such as monitors (lab equipment), where some data \
has to be updated continuously for hours or days. ", "Display" -> "markdown", 
    "Hash" -> "427c1c9f-5473-44c3-9f0b-685ad9b74c39", "Invisible" -> False, 
